    "Html": "In the Silverlight DataGrid there is an incompatible scrolling&nbsp;issue where it&nbsp;cannot use a ScrollViewer.&nbsp; Since the WPF DataGrid does use a ScrollViewer, the templates are slightly incompatible and changes would have to be made to the template to have it work for both.&nbsp; If you take a look at the generic.xaml file in the CTP source you can see what the default WPF DataGrid template looks like.&nbsp;\r\n",
